    <item>
      <title>洪氏称中国股市下跌“吸引力不足以”买入和成长投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/chinese-market-dip-not-attractive-enough-to-buy-hong-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Grow Investment Group 的洪浩表示，目前中国股市的下跌“不足以吸引我买入”，尤其是随着唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，“贸易战风险正在上升”。洪浩还告诉彭博电视台，投资者预计北京将在农历新年期间和 3 月的两会期间发布政策声明。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/chinese-market-dip-not-attractive-enough-to-buy-hong-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:28:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
