    <item>
      <title>美联储和关税押注导致亚洲货币指数跌至二十年来最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asian-currency-index-falls-to-two-decade-low-on-fed-tariff-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济强劲增长和当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提高关税的言论支撑美元，亚洲货币跌至二十年来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asian-currency-index-falls-to-two-decade-low-on-fed-tariff-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚太借款人掀起全球美元债券发售热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asia-pacific-borrowers-kick-off-rush-of-global-dollar-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚太地区的借款人开启了今年全球债券发行最繁忙的一周，这是对投资者信贷兴趣的一次关键考验，收益率溢价接近全球金融危机以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asia-pacific-borrowers-kick-off-rush-of-global-dollar-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东市场走强，油价维持在 10 月高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于亚洲炼油商的强劲需求，一些中东原油价格上涨，油价稳定在近三个月来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 23:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲货币跌至二十年来最低点，股市涨跌互现：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲货币兑美元的汇率跌至近二十年来的最低点，股市出现波动，芯片行业蓬勃发展的涨幅被日本的疲软所抵消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普给经济前景蒙上阴影，债券交易员认为未来一年形势严峻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/bond-traders-see-fraught-year-ahead-as-trump-shadows-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济的强劲复苏以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的减税和关税政策有可能使美国国债继续承压，债券交易员在进入新的一年时对前景的预期有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/bond-traders-see-fraught-year-ahead-as-trump-shadows-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊称特朗普的主要立法议程将在 5 月前通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/johnson-says-trump-s-major-legislative-agenda-will-pass-by-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊誓言，一项针对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普一系列优先事项的雄心勃勃的法案将于四月份在美国众议院获得表决通过，对于党派分歧较小的众议院来说，这是一个紧张的日程安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/johnson-says-trump-s-major-legislative-agenda-will-pass-by-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 17:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
